(390721, '22LR - No Confusion Please The 22 Long Rifle (22LR) is a unique cartridge. It is not to be confused with the 22 Winchester Magnum Rimfire (22 WMR), the 22 Hornet or other 22-sounding cartridges.\n \nIf shooting fun, versatility, cost and popularity of the cartridge are considerations, please forget the other so-called 22 cartridges and concentrate on the Number One - the 22LR. Over the past century (actually 124 years) many cartridges have come and gone; but, the 22LR still stands tall in popularity.\n \nUnless you have owned a 22LR or fired one, you dont know what fun you are missing. Why sit on the sidelines - buy one or trade your idle gun for one. If you finally do select a 22LR cartridge, your decision will be a wise one.', ''),
